name: Interactive Multi-Game Demo Disc Version 26
overview: Interactive Multi Game Demo Disc v26 (aka Monthly Nintendo Shop Demo - December 2003 in Japan) is a demo and video sampler disc, designed for retail store displays of the Nintendo GameCube. The sampler includes a simple menu and playable demos of Donkey Kong Jungle Beat, Star Fox: Assault, Resident Evil 4, Virtua Quest, and Metroid Prime 2: Echoes. The disc also features trailers of the following: Donkey Kong Jungle Beat, Resident Evil 4, Geist, Killer 7, NFL Street 2, Splinter Cell: Chaos Theory, Mortal Kombat: Deception, Star Fox: Assault, NBA Street V3, Dragon Ball Z: Sagas, and the Nintendo DS system.
